15#ifndef ISC_LIST_H
16#define ISC_LIST_H 1
17
18#include <isc/assertions.h>
19
20#ifdef ISC_LIST_CHECKINIT
21#define ISC_LINK_INSIST(x) ISC_INSIST(x)
22#else
23#define ISC_LINK_INSIST(x)
24#endif
25
26#define ISC_LIST(type) struct { type *head, *tail; }
27#define ISC_LIST_INIT(list) \
28 do { (list).head = NULL; (list).tail = NULL; } while (/*CONSTCOND*/0)
29
30#define ISC_LINK(type) struct { type *prev, *next; }
31#define ISC_LINK_INIT_TYPE(elt, link, type) \
32 do { \
33 (elt)->link.prev = (type *)(-1); \
34 (elt)->link.next = (type *)(-1); \
35 } while (/*CONSTCOND*/0)
36#define ISC_LINK_INIT(elt, link) \
37 ISC_LINK_INIT_TYPE(elt, link, void)
38#define ISC_LINK_LINKED(elt, link) ((void *)((elt)->link.prev) != (void *)(-1))
39
40#define ISC_LIST_HEAD(list) ((list).head)
41#define ISC_LIST_TAIL(list) ((list).tail)
42#define ISC_LIST_EMPTY(list) ((list).head == NULL)
43
44#define __ISC_LIST_PREPENDUNSAFE(list, elt, link) \
45 do { \
46 if ((list).head != NULL) \
47 (list).head->link.prev = (elt); \
48 else \
49 (list).tail = (elt); \
50 (elt)->link.prev = NULL; \
51 (elt)->link.next = (list).head; \
52 (list).head = (elt); \
53 } while (/*CONSTCOND*/0)
54
55#define ISC_LIST_PREPEND(list, elt, link) \
56 do { \
57 ISC_LINK_INSIST(!ISC_LINK_LINKED(elt, link)); \
58 __ISC_LIST_PREPENDUNSAFE(list, elt, link); \
59 } while (/*CONSTCOND*/0)
60
61#define ISC_LIST_INITANDPREPEND(list, elt, link) \
62 __ISC_LIST_PREPENDUNSAFE(list, elt, link)
63
64#define __ISC_LIST_APPENDUNSAFE(list, elt, link) \
65 do { \
66 if ((list).tail != NULL) \
67 (list).tail->link.next = (elt); \
68 else \
69 (list).head = (elt); \
70 (elt)->link.prev = (list).tail; \
71 (elt)->link.next = NULL; \
72 (list).tail = (elt); \
73 } while (/*CONSTCOND*/0)
74
75#define ISC_LIST_APPEND(list, elt, link) \
76 do { \
77 ISC_LINK_INSIST(!ISC_LINK_LINKED(elt, link)); \
78 __ISC_LIST_APPENDUNSAFE(list, elt, link); \
79 } while (/*CONSTCOND*/0)
80
81#define ISC_LIST_INITANDAPPEND(list, elt, link) \
82 __ISC_LIST_APPENDUNSAFE(list, elt, link)
83
84#define __ISC_LIST_UNLINKUNSAFE_TYPE(list, elt, link, type) \
85 do { \
86 if ((elt)->link.next != NULL) \
87 (elt)->link.next->link.prev = (elt)->link.prev; \
88 else { \
89 ISC_INSIST((list).tail == (elt)); \
90 (list).tail = (elt)->link.prev; \
91 } \
92 if ((elt)->link.prev != NULL) \
93 (elt)->link.prev->link.next = (elt)->link.next; \
94 else { \
95 ISC_INSIST((list).head == (elt)); \
96 (list).head = (elt)->link.next; \
97 } \
98 (elt)->link.prev = (type *)(-1); \
99 (elt)->link.next = (type *)(-1); \
100 ISC_INSIST((list).head != (elt)); \
101 ISC_INSIST((list).tail != (elt)); \
102 } while (/*CONSTCOND*/0)
103
104#define __ISC_LIST_UNLINKUNSAFE(list, elt, link) \
105 __ISC_LIST_UNLINKUNSAFE_TYPE(list, elt, link, void)
106
107#define ISC_LIST_UNLINK_TYPE(list, elt, link, type) \
108 do { \
109 ISC_LINK_INSIST(ISC_LINK_LINKED(elt, link)); \
110 __ISC_LIST_UNLINKUNSAFE_TYPE(list, elt, link, type); \
111 } while (/*CONSTCOND*/0)
112#define ISC_LIST_UNLINK(list, elt, link) \
113 ISC_LIST_UNLINK_TYPE(list, elt, link, void)
114
115#define ISC_LIST_PREV(elt, link) ((elt)->link.prev)
116#define ISC_LIST_NEXT(elt, link) ((elt)->link.next)
117
118#define __ISC_LIST_INSERTBEFOREUNSAFE(list, before, elt, link) \
119 do { \
120 if ((before)->link.prev == NULL) \
121 ISC_LIST_PREPEND(list, elt, link); \
122 else { \
123 (elt)->link.prev = (before)->link.prev; \
124 (before)->link.prev = (elt); \
125 (elt)->link.prev->link.next = (elt); \
126 (elt)->link.next = (before); \
127 } \
128 } while (/*CONSTCOND*/0)
129
130#define ISC_LIST_INSERTBEFORE(list, before, elt, link) \
131 do { \
132 ISC_LINK_INSIST(ISC_LINK_LINKED(before, link)); \
133 ISC_LINK_INSIST(!ISC_LINK_LINKED(elt, link)); \
134 __ISC_LIST_INSERTBEFOREUNSAFE(list, before, elt, link); \
135 } while (/*CONSTCOND*/0)
136
137#define __ISC_LIST_INSERTAFTERUNSAFE(list, after, elt, link) \
138 do { \
139 if ((after)->link.next == NULL) \
140 ISC_LIST_APPEND(list, elt, link); \
141 else { \
142 (elt)->link.next = (after)->link.next; \
143 (after)->link.next = (elt); \
144 (elt)->link.next->link.prev = (elt); \
145 (elt)->link.prev = (after); \
146 } \
147 } while (/*CONSTCOND*/0)
148
149#define ISC_LIST_INSERTAFTER(list, after, elt, link) \
150 do { \
151 ISC_LINK_INSIST(ISC_LINK_LINKED(after, link)); \
152 ISC_LINK_INSIST(!ISC_LINK_LINKED(elt, link)); \
153 __ISC_LIST_INSERTAFTERUNSAFE(list, after, elt, link); \
154 } while (/*CONSTCOND*/0)
155
156#define ISC_LIST_APPENDLIST(list1, list2, link) \
157 do { \
158 if (ISC_LIST_EMPTY(list1)) \
159 (list1) = (list2); \
160 else if (!ISC_LIST_EMPTY(list2)) { \
161 (list1).tail->link.next = (list2).head; \
162 (list2).head->link.prev = (list1).tail; \
163 (list1).tail = (list2).tail; \
164 } \
165 (list2).head = NULL; \
166 (list2).tail = NULL; \
167 } while (/*CONSTCOND*/0)
168
169#define ISC_LIST_PREPENDLIST(list1, list2, link) \
170 do { \
171 if (ISC_LIST_EMPTY(list1)) \
172 (list1) = (list2); \
173 else if (!ISC_LIST_EMPTY(list2)) { \
174 (list2).tail->link.next = (list1).head; \
175 (list1).head->link.prev = (list2).tail; \
176 (list1).head = (list2).head; \
177 } \
178 (list2).head = NULL; \
179 (list2).tail = NULL; \
180 } while (/*CONSTCOND*/0)
181
182#define ISC_LIST_ENQUEUE(list, elt, link) ISC_LIST_APPEND(list, elt, link)
183#define __ISC_LIST_ENQUEUEUNSAFE(list, elt, link) \
184 __ISC_LIST_APPENDUNSAFE(list, elt, link)
185#define ISC_LIST_DEQUEUE(list, elt, link) \
186 ISC_LIST_UNLINK_TYPE(list, elt, link, void)
187#define ISC_LIST_DEQUEUE_TYPE(list, elt, link, type) \
188 ISC_LIST_UNLINK_TYPE(list, elt, link, type)
189#define __ISC_LIST_DEQUEUEUNSAFE(list, elt, link) \
190 __ISC_LIST_UNLINKUNSAFE_TYPE(list, elt, link, void)
191#define __ISC_LIST_DEQUEUEUNSAFE_TYPE(list, elt, link, type) \
192 __ISC_LIST_UNLINKUNSAFE_TYPE(list, elt, link, type)
193
194#endif /* ISC_LIST_H */
